text: Resistencia Sport Club, is a Paraguayan football club based in Barrio Ricardo Brugada in Asunción. The club, founded on December 27, 1917 plays in the División Intermedia of The Paraguayan League. Resistencia S.C. plays its home matches at the Tomás Begon Gorea stadium. ==Honours== *Paraguayan Second Division: 4 ::1966, 1975, 1980, 1998 *Paraguayan Third Division: (runner-up) 1 ::2011 ==References== ==External links== *Resistencia SC Info Resistencia Resistencia Category:Association football clubs established in 1917 Category:1917 establishments in Paraguay
